{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243199, "create_time": 1655828414, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "还是说就是有意纵容，想让大家打打架？", "timestamp": 1655828414}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243213, "create_time": 1655828581, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 也许法律制定者的孩子不会受到校园暴力。（×）\n因为有未成年人保护法，而且校园暴力的程度有可能连唐山这次都算不上，咋判刑，一般就是口头教育。而且校园小混混光脚不怕穿鞋的，他们又不在乎自己的前途。\n我觉得真要立法不如拿老师和学校开刀，要求学校和老师防治校园暴力，处理不妥当会收到处罚", "timestamp": 1655828581}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243223, "create_time": 1655828671, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 要求学校和老师估计不行吧，学校和老师就像政府一样出了事天然选择维稳", "timestamp": 1655828671}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243236, "create_time": 1655828766, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 这种事情对未成年人的身心健康的影响不是小事，我们那边也确实发生过以死抗争，血溅五步的", "timestamp": 1655828766}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243243, "create_time": 1655828841, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 人家万一被判刑了，他的那帮兄弟混混不找你麻烦，他被放出来会报复呀", "timestamp": 1655828841}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243251, "create_time": 1655828917, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我当时就是不理他们，不跟他们有任何联系，我的几个哥们也身强体壮，不怕欺负。但有时候他们就是口臭或突然打无辜的同学，只好忍着呗，不然事情越大越麻烦", "timestamp": 1655828917}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243263, "create_time": 1655829141, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "感觉校园暴力缺乏监管是因为成人打架就懒得管，进一步原因可能是中国警力缺乏，只顾得过来杀人案件", "timestamp": 1655829141}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243265, "create_time": 1655829171, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 哈哈，是这样，校园暴力让我很早就对所谓公平正义，所谓法律有了清晰的认识，说到底不过是维稳的工具。也挺好哒。", "timestamp": 1655829171}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243297, "create_time": 1655829612, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "再进一步原因可能是中国不重视人权？除了活着之外的人权。“不就是打两下吗，又没有残疾和后遗症，过几天伤就好了”。家庭暴力也同样不管", "timestamp": 1655829612}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243345, "create_time": 1655830304, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "那么制止校园暴力的执行权放给谁呢？老师吗？体罚全面收紧了，现在老师管混混学生还剩啥手段啊", "timestamp": 1655830304}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243806, "create_time": 1655857554, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 啥都往人权上扯，看多了真下头。校园暴力和家庭暴力本来就难管，你只能遏制不能消除，国家又不是忽视这种问题。", "timestamp": 1655857554}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 243815, "create_time": 1655857809, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "未成年人保护法又保障未成年人所谓的人权，一般都不会从重处理，甚至刑事案件比如17岁女孩谋杀男童都会为了保护隐私封锁消息，这么严重的事情把它放到网上让舆论把她骂到紫砂不就行了吗/狗头", "timestamp": 1655857809}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 244035, "create_time": 1655864242, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Dave: 又装外宾喽", "timestamp": 1655864242}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 244874, "create_time": 1655883128, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 啊对对对，我外宾，您百姓", "timestamp": 1655883128}], "create_time": 1655828392, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": 